tables_create.lhc_mbird_channel: CREATE TABLE `lhc_mbird_channel` (`id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,`channel_id` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,`name` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci NOT NULL,`dep_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL, `created_at` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL, `updated_at` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,PRIMARY KEY (`id`), KEY `channel_id` (`channel_id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
